The evidence with the title 'Scathing fact-check: 'another year, another round of exaggeration ... ' says Jul 19, 2013  ... In his speech defending his health care law thursday , Obama said rebates averaging $100 are coming from insurance companies to 8.5 million Americans  ... In 2012 , 13 million rebates went out, in all 50 states. Another 8.5 (million) rebates are being sent out this summer, averaging around 100 bucks each. 
